	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<note>[Anfang ist abgeschnitten.]</note>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">[...]re <persName>Challon</persName>, vel <persName>Cabilonum</persName>, <persName>Schalun</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Dicitur <persName ref="p18465">regina Angliae</persName> misso fetiali indixisse bellum <persName ref="p20977">Guysianis</persName> pro <persName ref="p8315">Condensi</persName> et quod maximus equitatus et peditatus proficiscatur ex <placeName ref="l2477">Palatinatu</placeName>, <placeName ref="l749">Saxonia</placeName>, <placeName ref="l213">Hessia</placeName>, <placeName ref="l1750">Luneburgo</placeName> etc. in auxilium <persName ref="p8315">Condensis</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Confirmantur illa vera esse, quae scripsi de victoria domini ab <persName ref="p20637">Aderes</persName> et quod caesi sint aliquot <placeName ref="l473">Sangallenses</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Expectamus in horas alia nova, scimus et audimus caedes inaestimabiles fieri in <placeName ref="l832">Gallia</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Iam fama spargit redire <persName ref="p21320">abbatem Heremi</persName> ex concilio, dissolut m esse concilium, saltem ob famem et caritatem; nobis iterum negari forum ex <placeName ref="l306">Mediolano</placeName>, turbas <placeName ref="l55">Bononiae</placeName> excitari et nescio quid aliud.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de">Das wil ich glouben, wenn ichs grüntlicher von üch bericht wirt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Accepi 5. sessionem impressam et materiam 6. sessionis 17. septembris celebrandam.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">Si ergo potes, acquire mihi 2., 3., 4. sessionem; nihil gratius mihi obvenire posset.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la">Festinavi, male pinxi; boni consule.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale cum tuis et nostris omnibus.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la">21. augusti 1562.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la">Non relegi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la">Tuus, qui semper.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Darunter v. <persName ref="p8009">Fabricius</persName> die Notiz:]</note>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la">Verum esse affirmatur per idem tempus, quod d. <persName>de Susa</persName>, qui 8000 millibus <placeName ref="l2735">Provinciam</placeName> ingressus, fusus fugatusque sit a d. de <persName ref="p20637">Adreß</persName>, cuius copiae 4000 mille non multum excessere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la">Praestantissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8009">Ioanni Fabritio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae fideli ministro, domino et fratri colendo et dilecto.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l98">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
